high_descs: Turn right and go across the room to the chairs.
Pick up keys off of the middle chair.
Turn right and go forward across the room. Turn right and face the side table with the lamp on it.
Place the keys on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pair of keys to a side table.

high_descs: Turn around completely, then turn left and walk up to the middle chair.
Pick up the keys that are sitting on the chair.
Turn to the right and walk over to the left-hand side of the bedside table.
Place the keys down on the bedside table.
anns.task_desc: Move a set of keys to the bedside table.

high_descs: Move to the back of the room to the middle black chair
Pick up the keys on top of the chair
Carry the keys over to the round side table with the lamp on top of it
Place the keys on top of the table on the edge by the pencil
anns.task_desc: Move keys to the side table
